===Etymology===
From French ''[[gramme#French|gramme]]'', from [[Ancient Greek]] '''[[γραμμάριον]]''' (''grammarion'') "weight of two obols", from '''[[γραμμή]]''' (''gramme'') "line".

===Noun===
'''gram''' (''plural'' '''grams''')

# A unit of [[mass]] equal to one-[[thousandth]] of a [[kilogram]] (symbol: g)

